import React, { FC } from "react";
import { AddProductWrapper, BlockInputs, ButtonSubmit, InputAddProduct } from "./AddProduct.styled";

const AddProduct: FC = () => {
    

    return (
        <AddProductWrapper>

            добавление товара

            <BlockInputs>
                <InputAddProduct placeholder="name" />
                name
            </BlockInputs>
            <BlockInputs>
                <InputAddProduct placeholder="name" />
                categoryA
            </BlockInputs>
            <BlockInputs>
                <InputAddProduct placeholder="name" />
                tagsA
            </BlockInputs>
            <BlockInputs>
                <InputAddProduct placeholder="name" />
                length
            </BlockInputs>
            <BlockInputs>
                <InputAddProduct placeholder="name" />
                weight
            </BlockInputs>
            <BlockInputs>
                <InputAddProduct placeholder="name" />
                country
            </BlockInputs>
            <BlockInputs>
                <InputAddProduct placeholder="name" />
                price
            </BlockInputs>
            <BlockInputs>
                <InputAddProduct placeholder="name" type="file"/>
                picture
            </BlockInputs>
            <ButtonSubmit onClick={()=>{}}>добавить товар</ButtonSubmit>
        </AddProductWrapper>
    )
}

export default AddProduct;
